{"id":291525,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/维权网-中国选举观察（2013）之四――北京丰台区村/","date":"2013-05-01T21:00:43Z","modified":"2013-05-01T21:00:43Z","title":"维权网 | 中国选举观察（2013）之四――北京丰台区村官选举不民主","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员姚立法报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>日</span><span>，是北京市丰台区长辛店镇张家坟村新一届村委会重新选举日。此前的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>日</span><span>是该村新一届村委会投票选举日。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>日那天，选民中有不少人是非本村的农民，他们被人“请来”参加投票，随后被人告到了丰台区村民委员会选举工作指导办公室，经调查后，被宣布选举无效。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>张家坟村下属</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>个村民组，即二老庄、张家坟、马家坟、董家坟、吕村一、吕村二、吕村三。张家坟村农户</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">83 0 </span><span>多户，农业人口</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17 0 0</span><span>多人，</span><span> </span><span>选民</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1374</span><span>人。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>日选票上的正式候选人和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>日的完全一样。村委会主任候选人是吴强和刘春明，村委会委员候选人是吴正安、张序和谢正红。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>日</span><span>和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>日两场选举，会场都有不少区和镇上派来村里指导选举的国家工作人员。两次的会场都设在村部。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>日，会场设有秘密写票间，严禁委托投票，选民领取选票时，须凭选民证并要签字。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>两次选举都规定，凡参加选举投票者可领到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>元的“误工费”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>张家坟村的不少选民议论，虽然</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>日</span><span>的选举被宣布无效，不知丰台区政府会不会依照《北京市村民委员会选举办法》第三十八条的规定，打击破坏选举的人。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[8584,19196]}